value: Resident, especially forest and thick bush: Cameroon, Bioko - N Angola east to SW Ethiopia, E side of South Africa; records Sierra Leone, Liberia, Cape Province.
wide range of habitats associated w.forest or thick bush:interior & edge many forest types;esp.clearings, secdy growth & scrub;dense evergreen & deciduous thickets;also banaina groves etc

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
